# MoharazNX lean mode

Before coding, read `docs/ROADMAP.md` only (not full chat history).

## Per-step scope
- Backend: 1–2 tables, list + get + patch, seed in `init_db.py`
- Frontend: `lib/api/<domain>.ts`, `use-<domain>.ts`, wire list + detail only
- Skip dashboard wiring unless user asks
- Skip new STEP*.md files; append short block to `docs/CHANGELOG.md`

## Do not
- Read entire `mock-data/*.ts` files (grep types / read target component only)
- Read `../againerp/` docs unless blocked
- Run full `npm run build` unless user asks
- Explore with broad Task/explore agents for known patterns

